Perfect place for wind on face...

Tataka was just resting wings!

this year, it getting too hard to keep
up with harvest.

to get bruised and not be able to sell
on market!

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0006

If only Tataka had more helping
hands...

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0007
rows.name:
You going to help Tataka out?!
Ohh, that would be big help!

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0008
rows.name:
Tataka going to keep slack-
Err, resting here a bit longer!

rows.label: tlk42100121_07_msg0009

Hope friends can help get harvesting
all done smoothy-smooth!
